{
  "texts": [
    "To account for the varying contributions of each section to the overall summary, we followed the work of Ermakova et al.(2018) and Li & Xu (2023), assigning 30%, 25%, 30%, and 15%",
    "weights to the Background, Methods, Results, and Conclusions sections, respectively.",
    "As a result, the lengths of the Background, Methods, Results, and Conclusions sections were no more than 90, 75, 90, and 45 words, respectively.",
    "For GPT-4 (gpt-4-0613), we used the API provided by OpenAI, and input the source article with the prompt \"Summarize the following scientific paper no more than 300 words\", and the other parameters in the API are set to default values.",
    "Evaluation Metrics on the SFR task."
  ]
}